26:16.931 --> 26:29.743
Senate at their last meeting, I said, look, when 
this Senate is going, the first time I say to

26:16.931 --> 26:29.743
myself, Jesus Christ, why did I do this? You are a 
success. And it took about a year, but then I

26:32.744 --> 26:37.911
