station, which you would if you wanted to do

29:18.071 --> 29:29.226
research, where did your loyalty lie? It was with 
the man who had the money. And so it was a terrible

29:33.819 --> 29:35.241
mess. And the only solution, the obvious one I 
wanted to achieve, was to get it back to the

29:36.943 --> 29:47.855
university and have the system say a flag on it and 
