33:43.927 --> 33:52.577
with affection because I like Art, was he could 
never make a decision. Gordy came back from some

33:54.869 --> 34:01.458
meeting after we had been announced he was coming 
here, and he'd run into somebody from Georgia

33:54.869 --> 34:01.458
Tech. You know, he'd been at Georgia Tech before, 
