34:59.423 --> 35:09.192
you better recruit that Nobel laureate fast, 
because people are getting mad at the way you're

34:59.423 --> 35:09.192
recruiting all these highfalutin faculty 
members. But that made me feel good. That meant the

35:10.694 --> 35:13.676
board was concerned and knew what I was trying to 
do. Now, they might not like it, but they

35:13.977 --> 35:15.998
understood it. And Hanson understood it, and he 
explained it to them, what we were trying to do. So

35:21.539 --> 35:30.352
we got those two, and then I went after... Is Bum 
still... Bum is still chairman of the board. Then

35:30.372 --> 35:37.242
one day Perry called, and he said, how much do you 
really want to recruit a Nobel laureate? I said,

35:38.063 --> 35:39.385
pretty much, Perry. He said, well, I think we have a 
shot at Norman Borlaug. And oh my God, that was...

35:45.674 --> 35:49.960
Then we got Norman, as you know, And that was 
