35:52.265 --> 35:57.510
Barton in chemistry. And that was another great 
shot in the arm for us. And you know, my feeling was

36:02.775 --> 36:10.663
that if you could recruit at that level, Henry, you 
didn't have to worry about being a national

36:02.775 --> 36:10.663
institution anymore. Right. Or a world. That's 
